1. Will she be doing her homework at eight o'clock? 2. We will not be playing
chess the whole evening. 3. She says that they will be waiting for you at seven. 4. She
will be writing the letter while you are sweeping the floor. 5. I will be working the
whole evening tomorrow. 6. We will meet them when they are going to the institute.
7. When I come here, my children will be playing. 8. We will be baking a cake with
strawberries at five tomorrow. If you want just come. 9. When we come to school,
they will be doing the test. 10. I will be walking in the park since 7 till 8 o'clock.
